Maddo's Vim SEttings
--------------------

You can clone this git, or copy and paste the vimrc elements that you
like most into your own.

If you clone it, you can use symbolic links to keep it updated.
    ln -s /path/to/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
Make sure you backup your current vimrc first.

Create your custom settings in
    ~/vimrc_local
It will be automatically loaded by this vimrc.  Settings in the 
vimrc_local file should override the ones in the .vimrc


